cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MA, cs.SY, cs.CL 

This paper is about multi-agent reinforcement learning (MARL) and proposes a novel framework for communication among agents. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), which is the primary focus of the paper. The paper also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multi-agent systems (cs.MA) as it deals with the interaction and coordination of multiple agents. The paper also discusses the scalability and global cooperation capability of the proposed framework, which falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper uses graph neural networks for message propagation, which is a common technique in natural language processing (cs.CL).
